title: Regarding whether it will be popularized on a large scale
body: ENS is currently the leader in the domain name field, but with the rapid development of other public chains, ENS only chooses Ethereum as the underlying public chain, and its suffix is limited to the format of .eth, will it restrict its long-term development?
author: 0xAC0ea85F1C2f0B07E2862BA1CC4DA36150A4Faab
